rest in it,\\\" Orie says of his life before that particular conversation in 2016.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"conflict\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"any fighting\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"any interest\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"that particular conversation\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boxing, then, was not the obvious choice, and yet, eight years later, the family will be at theParis Olympicsthis summer to watch Orie attempt to win super-heavyweight gold for Team GB.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9998408702463593, \"rank\": 0.00014396959857937384, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boxing\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"the obvious choice\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympicsthis summer\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"Orie attempt\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"super-heavyweight gold\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will emulate his idol should he do so, with four minutes and 32 seconds ofAnthony Joshua's illustrious career having the potential to prove the genesis of another golden moment for British boxing.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"score\": 0.9999999995616236, \"rank\": 4.3821684426639365e-10, \"text\": \"Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\"}, {\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3001258468919187e-14, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his idol\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"four minutes\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"32 seconds\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"the genesis\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"another golden moment\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Less than two rounds; enough for Joshua to stop Charles Martin and become world champion in 2016, and for Orie to start dreaming.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 976, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"score\": 0.9999999995616236, \"rank\": 4.3821684426639365e-10, \"text\": \"Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\"}, {\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999999999399733, \"rank\": 6.006570664344455e-11, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world champion\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"Orie\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then 18, and having never previously heard of Joshua, he stumbled upon that bout and began researching.\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1120, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"score\": 0.9999999995616236, \"rank\": 4.3821684426639365e-10, \"text\": \"Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that bout\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Immediately inspired to follow the same path, Orie wanted to become Olympic champion before he had thrown a jab.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same path\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"Orie\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"a jab\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If it was just a brute who won a world title, I could not connect with that,\\\" the 26-year-old says.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1392, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a brute\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"a world title\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But Anthony Joshua brought professionalism.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1398, \"end\": 1412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"professionalism\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The way he conducts himself, his approach to training - that resonated with me.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The way\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"his approach\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It just happened to be boxing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Orie was at the time working several jobs at once - McDonald's and Sports Direct among his employers - to raise enough money to send himself to university.\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1618, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frasers_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sports Direct\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frasers_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frasers_Group\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orie\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"several jobs\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"once - McDonald\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"his employers\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"enough money\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"university\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Born to a Russian mother in Moscow, Orie arrived in the UK at the age of seven, not speaking any English.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9866917318304155, \"rank\": 0.010450838316516633, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1735, \"end\": 1741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.401777971300749e-13, \"text\": \"Moscow\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\"}, {\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9965897359192675, \"rank\": 0.0034219311486391227, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orie\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"any English\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teenage dreams of becoming a basketball player were derailed by not possessing a British passport, which prevented travel to the United States and then also left him ineligible for student finance.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_passport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British passport\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_passport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_passport\"}, {\"begin\": 1942, \"end\": 1955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996946562044541, \"rank\": 0.00030542626024809464, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Teenage dreams\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"a basketball player\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"student finance\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Mental strength therapy': Anthony Joshua returns to gym after car crash Itauma postpones Franklin fight after training injury Tyson Fury reveals major new update on boxing future after retirement Little masterpieces: The ING Discerning Eye exhibition returns \\\"It came from a place of anger, frustration and disappointment,\\\" Orie says of his determination to overcome those funding obstacles.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\"}, {\"begin\": 2141, \"end\": 2151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyson_Fury\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9127732338144518e-23, \"text\": \"Tyson Fury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyson_Fury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyson_Fury\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gym\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"car crash\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2084}, {\"ngram\": \"Itauma\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"major new update\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"future\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"retirement Little masterpieces\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"frustration\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointment\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2334}, {\"ngram\": \"his determination\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"those funding obstacles\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A first-class honours degree in Business and Management was his reward.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A first-class honours degree\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"Business\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"Management\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"his reward\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is an obvious temptation to lean into comparisons with Joshua; both came to the sport at 18, both have Nigerian fathers and, if the Team GB formula delivers again, both will hold an Olympic medal by the end of the summer.\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2543, \"end\": 2549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"score\": 0.9999999995616236, \"rank\": 4.3821684426639365e-10, \"text\": \"Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\"}, {\"begin\": 2591, \"end\": 2599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.9985791969875527, \"rank\": 0.0013752765001562768, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an obvious temptation\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"comparisons\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"the Team GB formula\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This, however, is not the same script dusted off for another reading.\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same script\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2747}, {\"ngram\": \"another reading\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If it wasn't for boxing, I could have been doing something else,\\\" Orie says.\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2858, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2805}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"Orie\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would have loved to have been a lecturer at a university.\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lecturer\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"a university\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Boxing did not save me.\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boxing\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boxing did not find me.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boxing\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I found it and I am using my attributes to excel in it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 3026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my attributes\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The super-heavyweight division has, even aside from Joshua, been a reliable source of Olympic medals for British fighters, stretching from Audley Harrison in 2000 to the likes of David Price, Joe Joyce and Frazer Clarke in more recent Games.\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3080, \"end\": 3086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"score\": 0.9999999995616236, \"rank\": 4.3821684426639365e-10, \"text\": \"Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\"}, {\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3001258468919187e-14, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 3167, \"end\": 3182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audley_Harrison\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Audley Harrison\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audley_Harrison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audley_Harrison\"}, {\"begin\": 3207, \"end\": 3218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Price_(baseball)\", \"score\": 0.9609106510710897, \"rank\": 0.0260915982659837, \"text\": \"David Price\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Price_(baseball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Price_(baseball)\"}, {\"begin\": 3220, \"end\": 3223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9999946482632782, \"rank\": 4.4441921995989284e-06, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 3224, \"end\": 3229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joyce_Summers\", \"score\": 0.8789144796618745, \"rank\": 0.137767124265225, \"text\": \"Joyce\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joyce_Summers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joyce_Summers\"}, {\"begin\": 3234, \"end\": 3247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frazer_Clarke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Frazer Clarke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frazer_Clarke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frazer_Clarke\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The super-heavyweight division\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3058}, {\"ngram\": \"a reliable source\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3110}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic medals\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3128}, {\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 3194, \"to\": 3203}, {\"ngram\": \"more recent Games\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not play boxing.\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have to be professional, live life like a monk Orie speaks with a quiet confidence when discussing the possibility of following suit, even as he acknowledges his range of emotions as Paris draws ever closer.\", \"from\": 3295, \"to\": 3509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3485, \"end\": 3490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992924131, \"rank\": 7.077589387697825e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"professional, live life\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3333}, {\"ngram\": \"a monk\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3345}, {\"ngram\": \"Orie\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"a quiet confidence\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3381}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"suit\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3431}, {\"ngram\": \"his range\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3466}, {\"ngram\": \"emotions\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would be lying to you if I said I was just excited, and that I am going to smack everybody and win,\\\" Orie admits.\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3627, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 3595, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"win\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's nerve-wracking.\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3650, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The whole world will be watching.\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The whole world\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I know that I am more than capable of getting that gold medal.\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that gold medal\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got the best team behind me, the best country behind me - we are going to do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best team\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3776}, {\"ngram\": \"the best country\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been offers to forgo the Olympics and turn professional, promoters keen to have discussions even since he took Commonwealth gold on home soil in 2022, but all have been swiftly knocked back.\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 4043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3964, \"end\": 3976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 6.678310002205336e-13, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3864}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3886}, {\"ngram\": \"promoters\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 3919}, {\"ngram\": \"discussions\", \"from\": 3933, \"to\": 3944}, {\"ngram\": \"home soil\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 3994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My dream really has been to represent Great Britain in the Olympics - that will mean everything,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4084, \"end\": 4097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999337916350214, \"rank\": 0.0006624397976136143, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My dream\", \"from\": 4046, \"to\": 4054}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4101, \"to\": 4113}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I am 70 years old and looking back, I know that being able to represent Team GB and win a medal for them will have made it a life worth living.\\\"\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4231, \"end\": 4238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9998408702463593, \"rank\": 0.00014396959857937384, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The plan is for Orie to enter the professional ranks after the Olympics, with time then of the essence for a man who does not seem himself in the sport beyond the age of 35.\", \"from\": 4305, \"to\": 4478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The plan\", \"from\": 4305, \"to\": 4313}, {\"ngram\": \"Orie\", \"from\": 4321, \"to\": 4325}, {\"ngram\": \"the professional ranks\", \"from\": 4335, \"to\": 4357}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4376}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4387}, {\"ngram\": \"the essence\", \"from\": 4396, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4417}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4456}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 4464, \"to\": 4471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's when you then have to think about how we are going to get to world-title level in that timeframe.\", \"from\": 4479, \"to\": 4584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world-title level\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4565}, {\"ngram\": \"that timeframe\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am looking to go all the way,\\\" Orie insists.\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Will he stick to that when ego and financial incentives present an appealing case to keep rolling the dice?\", \"from\": 4633, \"to\": 4740, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ego and financial incentives\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4688}, {\"ngram\": \"an appealing case\", \"from\": 4697, \"to\": 4714}, {\"ngram\": \"the dice\", \"from\": 4731, \"to\": 4739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is always fresh people ready to take your head off,\\\" he warns.\", \"from\": 4741, \"to\": 4810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fresh people\", \"from\": 4758, \"to\": 4770}, {\"ngram\": \"your head\", \"from\": 4785, \"to\": 4794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not play boxing.\", \"from\": 4811, \"to\": 4835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 4828, \"to\": 4834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have to be professional, live life like a monk.\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 4887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"professional, live life\", \"from\": 4851, \"to\": 4874}, {\"ngram\": \"a monk\", \"from\": 4880, \"to\": 4886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Completely sacrifice everything in your life.\", \"from\": 4888, \"to\": 4933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4909, \"to\": 4919}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 4923, \"to\": 4932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then you get to a certain age and think about what the next thing is.\\\"\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 5004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a certain age\", \"from\": 4950, \"to\": 4963}, {\"ngram\": \"the next thing\", \"from\": 4985, \"to\": 4999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These are decisions for another day, but his motivation for fighting brings us back to the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 5006, \"to\": 5112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 5016, \"to\": 5025}, {\"ngram\": \"another day\", \"from\": 5030, \"to\": 5041}, {\"ngram\": \"his motivation\", \"from\": 5047, \"to\": 5061}, {\"ngram\": \"fighting\", \"from\": 5066, \"to\": 5074}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5082, \"to\": 5084}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 5093, \"to\": 5111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most in Orie's position would speak with a tunnel vision, the fulfilling of an eight-year ambition on the horizon and the jeopardy of sport at the elite level an ineluctable danger, but there is a determination that he is not the only one for whom this proves a defining summer.\", \"from\": 5113, \"to\": 5391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orie's position\", \"from\": 5121, \"to\": 5136}, {\"ngram\": \"a tunnel vision\", \"from\": 5154, \"to\": 5169}, {\"ngram\": \"the fulfilling\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5185}, {\"ngram\": \"an eight-year ambition\", \"from\": 5189, \"to\": 5211}, {\"ngram\": \"the horizon\", \"from\": 5215, \"to\": 5226}, {\"ngram\": \"the jeopardy\", \"from\": 5231, \"to\": 5243}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 5247, \"to\": 5252}, {\"ngram\": \"an ineluctable danger\", \"from\": 5272, \"to\": 5293}, {\"ngram\": \"a determination\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5323}, {\"ngram\": \"a defining summer\", \"from\": 5373, \"to\": 5390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you are a kid, you do not notice inspiration,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 5393, \"to\": 5454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 5407, \"to\": 5412}, {\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 5432, \"to\": 5443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You just subconsciously believe.\", \"from\": 5455, \"to\": 5488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so powerful, it's insane.\", \"from\": 5489, \"to\": 5519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a real life walking example of it.\", \"from\": 5520, \"to\": 5559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a real life\", \"from\": 5525, \"to\": 5536}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 5545, \"to\": 5552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would love to do that to the younger generation.\", \"from\": 5561, \"to\": 5612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the younger generation\", \"from\": 5589, \"to\": 5611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kids and young adults just need somebody to tell them that things are possible.\", \"from\": 5613, \"to\": 5692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kids\", \"from\": 5613, \"to\": 5617}, {\"ngram\": \"young adults\", \"from\": 5622, \"to\": 5634}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 5645, \"to\": 5653}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 5672, \"to\": 5678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can completely change their life.\", \"from\": 5693, \"to\": 5729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their life\", \"from\": 5718, \"to\": 5728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have two aims at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 5730, \"to\": 5768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two aims\", \"from\": 5737, \"to\": 5745}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 5749, \"to\": 5767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First, win that medal, look good.\", \"from\": 5769, \"to\": 5802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that medal\", \"from\": 5780, \"to\": 5790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Second one is to inspire.\\\"\", \"from\": 5803, \"to\": 5829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aldi are proud Official Partners of Team GB & ParalympicsGB, supporting all athletes through to Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 5831, \"to\": 5938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5831, \"end\": 5835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aldi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\"}, {\"begin\": 5927, \"end\": 5937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1220098873384988e-20, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"proud Official Partners\", \"from\": 5840, \"to\": 5863}, {\"ngram\": \"Team GB\", \"from\": 5867, \"to\": 5874}, {\"ngram\": \"ParalympicsGB\", \"from\": 5877, \"to\": 5890}, {\"ngram\": \"all a